snippet.title: Marry Me- Thomas Rhett (Girl Version) Cover by Amber Whitehead
snippet.description:
Hey y'all!
I've been sitting on this one for a long time. It's always been a hobby of mine to change male versions into female versions, as I also did with Hotline Bling three years ago! (How has it already been that long!?) Anyways, I know how popular this song is, and I know how many of you ladies love it- so here is the girls version! I heard this from Elle Mears! Hope you love it!
Dont forget to follow my social medias! 
Instagram- @amberwhiteheadmusic 
Twitter- @amberlwhitehead 
Snapchat- amberlwhitehead
Facebook.com/amberwhiteheadmusic soundcloud.com/amberwhiteheadmusic
